## Technical Changes

### Backend

- **[app.py](file:///Users/base/Projects/zget/src/zget/server/app.py)**: Added `host` and `port` to [SettingsUpdate](file:///Users/base/Projects/zget/src/zget/server/app.py#67-71) and handled persistence.
- **[main.py](file:///Users/base/Projects/zget/src/zget/server/main.py)**: Loaded defaults from persistent config.
- **[app.py](file:///Users/base/Projects/zget/src/zget/server/app.py)**: Refined `/api/settings` to return a smarter, context-aware `local_ip`.

### Frontend

- **[app.js](file:///Users/base/Projects/zget/src/zget/server/static/components/app.js)**: Enlarged the Settings modal container.
- **[settings.js](file:///Users/base/Projects/zget/src/zget/server/static/components/settings.js)**: Redesigned the settings form with new network inputs.
- **[ingest.js](file:///Users/base/Projects/zget/src/zget/server/static/components/ingest.js)**: Styled the ingest input for transparency.
- **[ingest.js](file:///Users/base/Projects/zget/src/zget/server/static/components/ingest.js)**: Used high-specificity `!important` resets to nuke persistent theme borders on the input element.
- **[settings.js](file:///Users/base/Projects/zget/src/zget/server/static/components/settings.js)**: Added dynamic labeling for the Access URL (VPN vs LOCAL).

## Verification Results

- **Settings Persistence**: Confirmed that changes to Host/Port are correctly saved to `config.json`.
- **UI Audit**: Verified the "Amber/Gold" theme and layout improvements via browser screenshots.
- **Functionality**: Confirmed "Saved!" success state on committing changes.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> A server restart is required for changes to **Host** and **Port** to take effect.
